{"tid":751014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大劉講得啱，班廢青去少次旅行換少部電話，香港就唔會落得如斯田地","createTime":"2018-07-21T13:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T14:44:00.000Z","uid":29625,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bbcc167fb98facad5e0c77d4b23b7d7c3475fb77","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"去少次旅行，社會上層自然唔會戀棧權位，會退位俾後生仔上位<br />\n<br />\n換少部電話，六大產業就唔會淪為笑柄變晒金融地產項目，創科局都唔會咁垃圾<br />\n<br />\n睇少次戲，樓價同樓價收入比就唔會屢創全球紀錄，仲被國際調查機構評為「嚴重不可負擔」<br />\n<br />\n搭少次的士，衣食住行就唔會俾貴租帶動搞到樣樣貴，偏偏人工就唔貴<br />\n<br />\n買少件衫褲，香港貧富懸殊就唔會係世界第一，可以實現全民均富<br />\n<br />\n課少次金，政府就唔會寧願起大白象向中共獻媚，都唔擺錢落醫療體系<br />\n<br />\n篤少串魚蛋，大陸就唔會日日批150人落嚟排公屋，仲輸入「專才」同本地人爭工打<br />\n<br />\n出少次街食飯，政府政策自然就會以民生為依歸，而唔係基於官商勾結/政治目的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港有今時今日咁繁榮，都係靠阿叔當年窮到要食樹根食出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家啲廢青，連樹根都唔敢食，返工竟然仲夠膽死諗放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明香港今時今日搞成咁，都係班廢青造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成班死廢柴姓賴，唔負責不特止，仲淨係識怨天尤人推卸責任，抵鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a4d25d593b0507db30fe4467a236d30d0b2d17","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"嬲到開錯台，肯定又係死廢青影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad85cfac3541b92e8ebeef3887bbd0f5cf056eda","tid":751014,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"白銀外流邊個幫我買樓？"},{"pid":"b70e5bfb73232cc16f6781b38da7e11eefb8cf76","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad85cfac3541b92e8ebeef3887bbd0f5cf056eda","tid":751014,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"白銀外流邊個幫我買樓？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"你係咪恰阿叔唔識歷史疾鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以話而家啲廢青，無大無細，都唔識尊重長輩<br />\n我地嗰代人邊會咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e587d3fe5f411475e7ce5b53211acf7918e168","tid":751014,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"星矢陷阱"},{"pid":"1e5c306cd9e4e7c473b377be532e1f971a1ec131","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2e587d3fe5f411475e7ce5b53211acf7918e168","tid":751014,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"星矢陷阱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"咪話阿叔唔教精你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心你睇少啲卡通，用啲時間打多份pt<br />\n當你捱到入廠應該就儲夠錢買樓俾個仔架啦"},{"pid":"081ad3be1673b242c0eb40ac83bb7f818971abe1","tid":751014,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"香港三大原因，土地問題、廢青旅行、都係估中。<br />\n<br />\n以後有咩問題嘅成因都係咁！"},{"pid":"8a342534eebf154b986082c26ca19f06441dc984","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"081ad3be1673b242c0eb40ac83bb7f818971abe1","tid":751014,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"香港三大原因，土地問題、廢青旅行、都係估中。<br />\n<br />\n以後有咩問題嘅成因都係咁！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"根本係事實，廢青不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978f24f1a2b84ad2d1324038f6e0eb1748bcaeb0","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f75183506f57554caf12874a6f792a083c96bcc","tid":751014,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4200ba6919626de0452f2244f86c75a522471a","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"2隻廢青偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2e73a415cf4eef595c2202a51d52073b9c13c9","tid":751014,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}